seo: airflow,漏洞检测,未授权访问,在线扫描
summary: 该插件用于检测Airflow应用的未授权访问漏洞，通过发送HTTP请求并分析响应内容来判断是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect unauthorized access vulnerabilities in the Airflow application by sending HTTP requests and analyzing the response content to determine if there are any vulnerabilities.
